page.title: 20LIFESTYLES IN WIS. GREEN 2
page.content: We get up about half past six. We have a slice of toast and a cup of tea. Next we work on the nursery until lunch when we have beefburgers, baked beans and chips. After lunch we go back and work on the nursery. Then we go in and have salad, a cup of tea and some cakes. After tea we go and watch some television programmes. Then we get ready to go to Selsey where our Mum's caravan is kept. First we go to the pub for about an hour and then we go to the burger bar for something to eat. We go to bed at twelve o'clock.
